---
layout: default
title: Connecting the Dots Blog
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
socialSnippet: Showing how small efforts can cascade into big changes for our communities.
---

<main class="space-y-8 md:space-y-16">
    <header class="pt-8 space-y-4">
        <h1 class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-4xl leading-snug tracking-wide text-center font-display">
            <span class="text-hue">{{blogPage.blogName}}:</span> {{blogPage.introText}}
        </h1>
        <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto prose text-center">
            <div class="leading-normal">{{blogPage.callForWriters | markdownify | safe }}</div>
        </div>
    </header>
<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 sm:grid-cols-12">
    {% for item in collections.blog %}
        <li class="sm:col-start-2 sm:col-span-10">
            {% include "components/_blog-card.njk" %}
        </li>
    {% endfor %}
</ul>
    {% include "components/_footer.njk" %}

</main>
